<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Sustaining Member (Annual Membership)</span><br /><span>Make an initial gift of $1,000 or more (all at once or in monthly installments) to any BYU-Idaho fundraising priority within a 12-month period.&nbsp; Membership is renewed annually with a gift of $1,000 or more.</span></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Heritage Member (Lifetime Membership)</span><br />Make a gift of $25,000 or more (cash or gift-in-kind).</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Deferred Gifts</span><br />Planned gifts to BYU-Idaho through wills and trusts qualify for membership in the BYU-Idaho Legacy Society.&nbsp; Some deferred gifts may also qualify for membership in the President's Club.</p>
<p>For more information, please speak with a donor liaison at BYU-Idaho's office of LDS Philanthropies.&nbsp; They may be reached at (208) 496-3510 or (800) 227-4257.</p>
